    "MissionGiver": "Ling Family Hauling",
    "Title": "Ling Family ~mission(ReputationRank) Cargo Haul - ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Scale",
    "DisplayTitle": "Ling Family Rookie Cargo Haul - Medium Scale",
    "Description": "Hi, \n\nGuess the folks at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4> are planning a party and need help acquiring everything in a timely manner. You\u2019ll need to make multiple pick-ups for this one, including one in Nyx to grab some Jynx gin. Not sure if you\u2019ve ever had the stuff, but it\u2019s a Nyx specialty. Some folks can\u2019t get past that it glows pink, but I love it. Got a truly unique kick to it.\n\nHere are the pick ups:  \n\nPICK UP LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER) \n\n~mission(MultiToSingleToken)     \n\nPlease remember to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4>, as you\u2019ll be handling cargo containers up to <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4>.  \n\n  \nHappy Hauling,  \nReyes Ling \nCargo Logistics Coordinator \nLing Family Hauling\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nLing Family Hauling knows it\u2019s a dangerous and unpredictable universe and has established several protocols to protect both you and our client\u2019s cargo. To ensure you aren\u2019t punished for circumstances outside of your control, total payment will be prorated to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered. A delivery timer will be set for each haul. Any cargo that remains undelivered upon its expiration will be flagged as stolen and treated as such. All pick-ups and deliveries must be autoloaded or done at a freight elevator.",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi, \n\nGuess the folks at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4> are planning a party and need help acquiring everything in a timely manner. You\u2019ll need to make multiple pick-ups for this one, including one in Nyx to grab some Jynx gin. Not sure if you\u2019ve ever had the stuff, but it\u2019s a Nyx specialty. Some folks can\u2019t get past that it glows pink, but I love it. Got a truly unique kick to it.\n\nHere are the pick ups:  \n\nPICK UP LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER) \n\n[MultiToSingleToken]     \n\nPlease remember to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4>, as you\u2019ll be handling cargo containers up to <EM4>8 SCU</EM4>.  \n\n  \nHappy Hauling,  \nReyes Ling \nCargo Logistics Coordinator \nLing Family Hauling\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nLing Family Hauling knows it\u2019s a dangerous and unpredictable universe and has established several protocols to protect both you and our client\u2019s cargo. To ensure you aren\u2019t punished for circumstances outside of your control, total payment will be prorated to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered. A delivery timer will be set for each haul. Any cargo that remains undelivered upon its expiration will be flagged as stolen and treated as such. All pick-ups and deliveries must be autoloaded or done at a freight elevator.",
